verbose_text: The PCR amplification of GNRHR2 was performed using forward (F-CCCCGGACAAGGAAGGG) and reverse (R-AAGGAGCGACGGAGGGTCAA) primers (Integrated DNA Technologies, Coralville, Iowa) as well as a FAM labeled TaqMan MGB probe (ATGATGCCCCTGCCGG; Applied Biosystems, Foster City, CA).
